{"tid":625970,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"而家疤迷仲傷心過祖迷","createTime":"2018-04-11T21:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T08:36:00.000Z","uid":2974,"like":185,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9bbff9cb159af45ac301721be9cef8c0a500225f","tid":625970,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T21:07:29.000Z","msg":"皇馬出局，可以大抽特抽<br />\n皇馬加時/12碼贏，繼續潛水<br />\n而家難得祖記入到3粒，疤迷攞住個keyboard蠢蠢欲動，點知祖記自爆仲要最憎嘅牙朗做英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定谷住道氣谷到內傷，唯有試圖屈鳩人黑哨，不過佢地好似唔記得左以前自己點樣黑鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9855e4844f393c981a66771ea516a669ad558138","tid":625970,"uid":9009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T21:08:17.000Z","msg":"俾佢地靜下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642c4e5cd8706c31b6243105e9f9090538724e12","tid":625970,"uid":59357,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T21:11:57.000Z","msg":"好撚慘 成班疤狗會唔會有精神病 情緒失控架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好擔心佢地"},{"pid":"65c56bf50b2b49fb090ea905011bf14cb2b941f6","tid":625970,"uid":2974,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T21:19:59.000Z","msg":"其實未踢之前全世界包括疤迷都覺得皇會晉級架啦，點知祖記用左90分鐘幫佢地劣鳩，而家咁嘅結果對反疤黎講真係最佳劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a4de80adb09881cdaf796d7da69b4abb6414e4","tid":625970,"uid":82448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T21:26:03.000Z","msg":"又講得幾生動"},{"pid":"4cea0dc453cee41176a5b78383c1f48efbf6eea0","tid":625970,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T21:28:48.000Z","msg":"不要再撚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f3d9b97397d7ff22ffad11d65f699ba28c767c","tid":625970,